column5: New fishing lure looking for some help https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1209601435/zworm?ref=newest

Looking for my personal money? Bahahahaha. Yep, good luck. Can't believe crowdfunding works...can't believe people "invest" (read: give away money) in things without getting equity or tax breaks.  Looks like a decent lure, however.
Interesting looking lure. Looks like its got potential. Good luck with the project!

Your not really giving your money away rod. If it goes into production you are charged what you "donate" But will receive product. Therefore think of it as a pre order   and yes they do work very well
If I donate, do I get a lure in return?
Real worms have been proven for over a hundred years and they are FREE
